The Architectural Boundary

From GOLDEN_VISION_V2.md (Principle 1):

▌ "The provider's job is translation — converting between the Amplifier protocol and the Copilot SDK... It does not manage retry
▌ logic (kernel policy), context windows (orchestrator concern), tool execution (always denied)"

The empty read_file {} calls you saw are tool execution validation failures, not provider failures. The provider's Deny + Destroy
pattern means it never even sees these tool calls — it denies ALL tool execution from the SDK.

